<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Declaration Letter - Multi Party</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .page {
            background-color: white;
            width: 210mm;
            min-height: 297mm;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: relative;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .border-frame {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border: 2px dotted #333;
            padding: 4px;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .pattern-border {
            flex-grow: 1;
            border: 1px double #333;
            padding: 40px 50px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* Standard Frame lines as per reference */
        .page::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 5px;
            left: 5px;
            right: 5px;
            bottom: 5px;
            border: 2px solid #555;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .page::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            left: 10px;
            right: 10px;
            bottom: 10px;
            border: 4px double #555;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* Standard Watermark */
        .watermark {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 80%;
            opacity: 0.1;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .watermark img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .content-area {
            font-size: 11pt;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #000;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        /* Standard Header Logo */
        .logo-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .header-logo {
            height: 80px;
            width: auto;
        }

        .main-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: underline;
            font-size: 15pt;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .date-line {
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 11pt;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: underline;
            font-size: 13pt;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        /* Table Styling */
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 10.5pt;
        }

        table,
        th,
        td {
            border: 1px solid black;
        }

        th {
            padding: 8px 5px;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }

        td {
            padding: 8px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .col-sl {
            width: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .col-gst {
            width: 120px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .bold {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        @media (max-width: 850px) {
            .page {
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
            }

            .pattern-border {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="page">
        <div class="border-frame">
            <div class="pattern-border">

                <!-- Standard Watermark -->
                <div class="watermark">
                    <img src="images/webel.png" alt="Watermark">
                </div>

                <div class="content-area">

                    <!-- Standard Header Logo -->
                    <div class="logo-container">
                        <img src="images/webel.png" alt="Webel Logo" class="header-logo">
                    </div>

                    <div class="main-title">Declaration Letter</div>

                    <div class="date-line">
                        Date: <%= data?._current_date %>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Body Para 1 -->
                    <p>
                        On behalf as duly authorised & having competence to do so, we declare that the Project Report as
                        submitted, is covered under IT & ITeS activities as notified by IT&E dept. vide notification
                        <span class="bold">
                            <%= data?._it_notification_no %>
                        </span> dated <span class="bold">
                            <%= data?._it_notification_date %>
                        </span> (UDIN: <span class="bold">
                            <%= data?._it_notification_udin %>
                        </span>). We shall indemnify and hold the state harmless, including all associated costs in case
                        of any misrepresentation.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Body Para 2 -->
                    <p>
                        We also understand that any kind of misrepresentation will invite legal action as per law.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Table Section -->
                    <div class="section-title">Applicants Details</div>

                    <table>
                        <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th class="col-sl">Sl No.</th>
                                <th style="width: 25%;">Applicants Name</th>
                                <th>Address</th>
                                <th class="col-gst">GSTN/PAN Number</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <% if (data?._applicants && data?._applicants.length> 0) { %>
                                <% data?._applicants.forEach(function(applicant, index) { %>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td class="col-sl">
                                            <%= index + 1 %>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="bold">
                                            <%= applicant?._name %>
                                        </td>
                                        <td>
                                            <%= applicant?._address %>
                                        </td>
                                        <td class="col-gst">
                                            <%= applicant?._tax_id %>
                                        </td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <% }); %>
                                        <% } else { %>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td colspan="4" style="text-align: center;">No applicant details found.
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <% } %>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>